<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pesanan Berhasil</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #1e293b;
            --bg-card: #334155;
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --success: #22c55e;
            --accent: #f59e0b;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-main);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .success-card {
            background-color: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .icon-wrapper {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background-color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0 auto 24px;
        }

        .icon-wrapper i {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: var(--success);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: var(--success);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .info-box {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .btn-new {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-main);
            padding: 14px 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-new:active {
            background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-card">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>
        </div>
        <h1>Pesanan Diterima!</h1>
        <p>Pesanan Anda telah langsung masuk ke sistem kasir kami. Kami akan segera menyiapkannya untuk Anda.</p>
        
        <div class="info-box">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-bell-concierge"></i>
            Silakan tunggu di meja Anda
        </div>

        <button class="btn-new" onclick="window.history.back()">Kembali ke Menu</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>